Interface SelectableContentMessageContainer<T extends Message>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of message in this container
    All Superinterfaces:

    public interface SelectableContentMessageContainer<T extends Message>
extends SingleMessageContainer<T>, MessageLocationProducer, MessageLocationHighlighter
    A SingleMessageContainer that allows to select content, that is, produces message locations and it's also capable of highlight.
